cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.COM 

This paper is primarily focused on the information theory aspects of massive MIMO, specifically on the impact of pilot contamination on spectral efficiency. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). However, since the paper also discusses signal processing and communication network aspects, it could also be categorized under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.COM (Computer Communications and Networks). Additionally, since the paper deals with the use of large antenna arrays, it could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, since the paper discusses the impact of channel models and covariance matrices, it could also be categorized under cs.SI (Signal Processing).
